		<profileDesc>
			<abstract>
				<p>We propose a method for the fast estimation of hyperparameters in large networks, based on the linear response relation in the cavity method, and an empirical measurement of the Green&apos;s function. Simulation results show that it is efficient and precise, when compared with cross-validation and other techniques which require matrix inversion.</p>
